Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:41.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたを照らした光彩がわたしの記憶にも在るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:52.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てを証明していこう存在していく為の理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside of Kaos I say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:55.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where can I get the real love and fate，right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How can I make you know my heart is with you hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:05.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}人間は誰も忘れていく痛めた傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:12.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:17.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.06,0:24:18.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Back and forth　心中叫んでやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:22.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:27.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:27.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.37,0:24:30.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I can't live life without you by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:34.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「I'll believe」孤独も因縁さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:34.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Yeah，yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.27,0:24:37.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灼熱の記録の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.71,0:24:40.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来を映すbrightness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.41,0:24:40.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can see your light
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:47.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたを照らした光彩がわたしの記憶にも在るから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.43,0:24:48.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'm sure that we can go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:50.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てを証明していこう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.89,0:24:58.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}共存していく未来を　「I'll believe」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.18,0:24:57.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Yeah l'll believe
